<div class="modal-body">
  <p>Here are a few things to know about this CMT:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The first visible image will be the default image for a product.</li>
    <li>A product must have at least one image for it to display on the site.</li>
    <li>The image and caption attributes are required.</li>
    <li>The visibility of a <%= singular_resource %> on the front-end of the website can be controlled via the hide/show buttons in the list view.</li>
    <li>Sorting is controlled via drag-and-drop in the list view.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
